profile_summary: Detail-oriented and highly organized Warehouse Assistant with over 3 years of experience in inventory management, order fulfillment, and customer service. Proven ability to manage warehouse operations efficiently, maintain accurate records, and ensure timely delivery of goods. Committed to maintaining a safe and clean work environment, adhering to strict compliance with safety protocols.

description: Managed inventory and maintained accurate records of goods.
Handled order fulfillment processes efficiently to ensure timely delivery.
Provided excellent customer service, addressing queries and resolving issues promptly.
Maintained a clean and safe work environment, adhering to strict safety protocols.
Worked collaboratively with the team to meet warehouse objectives.
Assisted in the loading and unloading of goods, ensuring minimal damage.
achievements: Successfully reduced order fulfillment time by 15% through efficient management and organization.
